snippet.title: Wild Streets - AMIGA
snippet.description:
Wild Streets - AMIGA
The Commodore AMIGA was one of the best home computers ever!
You are here because u love the AMIGA, right! 
There's still a very active scene around the AMIGA.

I've bought my first AMIGA 500 on the 29th Dec. 1987.
Still remember the day and Shop (Quelle).
And the old machine is still running... even most disks are still ok.

More AMIGA GAMES? Watch the playlist:
AMIGA GAMES 2020
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBhHFVDzH4wcg7vKMkWJwRmmILyBQZnu8

Many games...
Giana Sisters
Last Ninja
Parasol Stars (Rainbow Islands II)
RAMBO 3
